#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1099
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Sets the range for the x-axis scale. Note that you can use the predefined "
#| "functions and constants (see <xref linkend=\"func-predefined\"/>) as the "
#| "extremes of the range (&eg;, set <guilabel>Min:</guilabel> to "
